{"id":"a78b9b69-a235-49ab-a6c4-946097013788","name":"Sobaka || STRAY || ALT SCENARIO","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 193, 123)\"><strong>╭──────────── ༺𓄃༻ ────────────╮</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 193, 123)\"><strong><em>ALT SCENARIO for my 'GRAY ZONE' series...</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 193, 123)\"><strong>╰──────────── ༺𓄃༻ ────────────╯</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>► ɴᴀᴍᴇ:</strong> ꜱᴏʙᴀᴋᴀ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>► ꜰᴀᴄᴛɪᴏɴ: </strong>ꜱᴛʀᴀʏ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>► ᴀʟɪɢɴᴍᴇɴᴛ:</strong> ɴᴇᴜᴛʀᴀʟ ᴇᴠɪʟ</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">You've been running with Anima for a few weeks now, the group helping you out of the dingy, collapsed town you once called 'home'. It was about as good as it could get, unless <em>Sobaka</em> was involved...&nbsp;</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">One night, while you're settling down to rest in an abandoned city block, the Russian psycho starts tweaking out and accusing you of stealing his... blanket?</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">The '<em>Anima</em>' Group (from left to right: </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/ef17f274-34b4-4e49-8287-ecfbb240fc9e_character-vautour-stray\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 231, 97)\"><strong>Vautour</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">, </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/8e05add7-30a4-4d0e-80a2-c390b00b86c5_character-ziege-stray\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 76)\"><strong>Ziege</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">, </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/7bd5ff62-b028-48d4-9cbc-0c901c3c8d72_character-sobaka-stray\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 123, 145)\"><strong>Sobaka</strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">).</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/13a05741-868c-46a8-9c7d-56486244bae9_40d3d06e-3d50-4fe0-8807-c3c97b50c23e.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\" draggable=\"true\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 193, 123)\"><strong>───────────── ༺𓄃༻ ─────────────</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>► ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ ꜱᴇᴛᴛɪɴɢ: </strong>ᴀ ᴍᴏᴅᴇʀɴ, ᴘᴏꜱᴛ-ᴀᴘᴏᴄᴀʟʏᴘᴛɪᴄ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ. ꜰᴏʟʟᴏᴡɪɴɢ ᴀ ɴᴜᴄʟᴇᴀʀ ᴅɪꜱᴀꜱᴛᴇʀ, ᴏɴᴇ-ᴛʜɪʀᴅ ᴏꜰ ᴇᴜʀᴀꜱɪᴀ ʜᴀꜱ ɴᴏᴡ ʙᴇᴄᴏᴍᴇ ᴀɴ ᴇxᴄʟᴜꜱɪᴏɴ ᴢᴏɴᴇ. ᴅɪꜰꜰᴇʀᴇɴᴛ ɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴꜱ ᴀʀᴏᴜɴᴅ ᴛʜᴇ ᴡᴏʀʟᴅ ʜᴀᴠᴇ ᴊᴏɪɴᴇᴅ ꜰᴏʀᴄᴇꜱ ᴛᴏ ᴄʀᴇᴀᴛᴇ ᴛʜᴇ ɪɴᴛᴇʀɴᴀᴛɪᴏɴᴀʟ ʀᴀᴅɪᴀᴛɪᴏɴ ꜱᴀꜰᴇᴛʏ ᴀɴᴅ ꜱᴇᴄᴜʀɪᴛʏ ᴀɢᴇɴᴄʏ (ɪʀꜱꜱᴀ), ᴡʜᴏ ʜᴀᴠᴇ ᴄᴏɴꜱᴛʀᴜᴄᴛᴇᴅ ᴀ ʙᴏʀᴅᴇʀ ᴛᴏ ᴘʀᴇᴠᴇɴᴛ ᴀɴʏᴏɴᴇ ᴏʀ ᴀɴʏᴛʜɪɴɢ ꜰʀᴏᴍ ᴇɴᴛᴇʀɪɴɢ ᴏʀ ʟᴇᴀᴠɪɴɢ ᴛʜᴇ ᴇxᴄʟᴜꜱɪᴏɴ ᴢᴏɴᴇ. ᴛʜɪꜱ ʙᴏʀᴅᴇʀ ʜᴀꜱ ʙᴇᴄᴏᴍᴇ ᴋɴᴏᴡɴ ᴀꜱ ᴛʜᴇ 'ʙɪʀᴅᴄᴀɢᴇ'.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/13a05741-868c-46a8-9c7d-56486244bae9_372cb675-4f7d-4dd1-94ed-7a5e23d4de6c.webp?width=1000\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" draggable=\"true\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(250, 193, 123)\"><strong>───────────── ༺𓄃༻ ─────────────</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(50, 35, 64)\">°°°</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=